(------------------------------------------------------------------------) show newline
() show newline
() show newline
(  Term      Meaning                                                ) show newline
(  memo      Any document in the Library of Cyberspace              ) show newline
(  RFC       A memo published in RFC format with canonical number   ) show newline
(  pen       To author a memo                                       ) show newline
(  promote   To elevate scope \(local > federation > core\)           ) show newline
() show newline
